@startuml SD_09_ChatSession
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - Chat Trực tiếp (Live Chat)
' FR-29, FR-30: Tạo phiên chat + Gửi/Nhận tin nhắn
' ============================================================

title **SD-09: Chat Trực tiếp\n(Live Chat Session)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E0F7FA
    ParticipantBorderColor #00838F
    ArrowColor #00838F
}

actor "Attendee" as Customer #LightBlue
participant "Customer\nBrowser" as CustBrowser #LightYellow
participant "ChatServlet\n(Controller)" as Controller #E0F7FA
participant "ChatService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "ChatDAO" as DAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5
participant "Organizer\nBrowser" as OrgBrowser #LightYellow
actor "Organizer" as Organizer #Gold

== Bước 1: Attendee khởi tạo Chat ==

Customer -> CustBrowser: Click "Chat với BTC"\ntrên trang sự kiện
CustBrowser -> Controller: POST /chat/create\n{eventId, organizerId}
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: getOrCreateSession(\ncustomerId, organizerId, eventId)
activate Service

Service -> DAO: findExistingSession(\ncustomerId, organizerId, eventId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM ChatSessions\nWHERE customerId = ?\nAND organizerId = ?\nAND eventId = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: ChatSession or null
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: result
deactivate DAO

alt Session already exists
    Service -> Service: Reuse existing session
else No existing session
    Service -> DAO: create(ChatSession)
    activate DAO
    DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO ChatSessions\n(sessionId, customerId,\norganizerId, eventId,\nstatus='active', createdAt)
    activate DB
    DB --> DAO: sessionId
    deactivate DB
    DAO --> Service: new ChatSession
    deactivate DAO
end

Service -> DAO: getMessages(sessionId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM ChatMessages\nWHERE sessionId = ?\nORDER BY createdAt ASC
activate DB
DB --> DAO: List<ChatMessage>
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: messages (history)
deactivate DAO

Service --> Controller: {session, messages}
deactivate Service
Controller --> CustBrowser: Forward → chat.jsp\n(session, messages, event info)
deactivate Controller
CustBrowser --> Customer: Cửa sổ chat mở\n(lịch sử tin nhắn cũ nếu có)

== Bước 2: Gửi tin nhắn (Attendee → Organizer) ==

Customer -> CustBrowser: Nhập tin nhắn + Gửi
CustBrowser -> Controller: POST /chat/send\n{sessionId, message, senderRole}
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: sendMessage(\nsessionId, senderId, message, role)
activate Service

Service -> DAO: createMessage(msg)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO ChatMessages\n(messageId, sessionId,\nsenderId, senderRole,\nmessage, createdAt)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: Created
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: ChatMessage
deactivate DAO

' --- Create Notification for Organizer ---
Service -> DB: INSERT INTO Notifications\n(userId=organizerId,\ntype='NEW_CHAT_MESSAGE',\nmessage='Tin nhắn mới từ {name}')

Service --> Controller: Message sent
deactivate Service
Controller --> CustBrowser: JSON {success: true,\nmessage: ChatMessage}
deactivate Controller
CustBrowser -> CustBrowser: Append message to chat UI\n(align right, timestamp)
CustBrowser --> Customer: ✅ Tin nhắn đã gửi

== Bước 3: Organizer nhận & trả lời ==

note over OrgBrowser
  AJAX Polling mỗi 3 giây
  kiểm tra tin nhắn mới
end note

OrgBrowser -> Controller: GET /chat/messages\n?sessionId={id}&after={lastMsgId}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: getNewMessages(\nsessionId, afterId)
activate Service
Service -> DAO: findMessagesAfter(\nsessionId, afterId)
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM ChatMessages\nWHERE sessionId = ?\nAND messageId > ?\nORDER BY createdAt ASC
activate DB
DB --> DAO: New messages
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: messages
deactivate DAO
Service --> Controller: messages
deactivate Service
Controller --> OrgBrowser: JSON {messages: [...]}
deactivate Controller
OrgBrowser -> OrgBrowser: Render tin nhắn mới\n(notification sound/badge)
OrgBrowser --> Organizer: 🔔 Tin nhắn mới

Organizer -> OrgBrowser: Nhập phản hồi + Gửi
OrgBrowser -> Controller: POST /chat/send\n{sessionId, message,\nsenderRole: "organizer"}
activate Controller
Controller -> Service: sendMessage(...)
activate Service
Service -> DB: INSERT ChatMessage\n+ Notification cho customer
Service --> Controller: OK
deactivate Service
Controller --> OrgBrowser: JSON {success: true}
deactivate Controller
OrgBrowser --> Organizer: ✅ Đã gửi

== Customer nhận phản hồi (Polling) ==

CustBrowser -> Controller: GET /chat/messages\n?sessionId={id}&after={lastId}
activate Controller
Controller --> CustBrowser: JSON {messages: [organizer reply]}
deactivate Controller
CustBrowser -> CustBrowser: Render phản hồi\n(align left, avatar BTC)
CustBrowser --> Customer: 💬 Phản hồi từ BTC

@enduml
